<item>
            <title>[HBASE-3980] assembly should not be bound to package lifecycle</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3980</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The current binding slows down significantly tasks like &apos;mvn install&apos; when you just want to push hbase JAR to the local maven cache.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12509888">HBASE-3980</key>
            <summary>assembly should not be bound to package lifecycle</summary>
